{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I said, I tell you, if you don't-- if you do that, you will be dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "OK, so what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He lied down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most-- most of the people lied down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't say most, but big numbers lied down in the snow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they froze to death for sure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I was up again all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was my third night up without any sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the walk, I think I must have slept while I was walking, just a few seconds now and then.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so the snow, in the morning SS, new SS men came after breakfast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had their good breakfast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they slept in their bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE] live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all these frozen people [LAUGHS] spending-- that's-- spending 12 hours, in minus 20 in the snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Imagine how bright people felt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And now, I had to go, had to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And other people were left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They just went around for 10, 15 minutes shooting all the people who were already probably dead anyhow, but just to make sure that not one should fall into the Russian hands.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to march all day again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now comes miracle number maybe six or seven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were marching all day on the highway, which was leading between big forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were approaching the Polish-Czechoslovak border, and near a town called Rybnik.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were approaching the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the-- in those mountains, again, we were away from the plains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were going up hill in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was getting very, very tired, very, very exhausted, maybe from lack of sleep or maybe from tiredness or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was in the middle of the column.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
